main event: A light-colored cigar-shaped object was sighted in Tacoma, Washington on 27 August 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed for 5 to 10 minutes,The object was visible about a hundred feet above the buildings,The course of the object was towards the north,It appeared with black clouds visible below it,The object made no sound and had no discernible features.
witness description: Reverend Fair, a minister with fair reliability
